      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 4 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 4 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蒙，亨。匪我求童蒙，童蒙求我。初筮告，再三瀆，瀆則不告。利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Meng (indicates that in the case which it presupposes) there will be progress and success. I do not (go and) seek the youthful and inexperienced, but he comes and seeks me. When he shows (the sincerity that marks) the first recourse to divination, I instruct him. If he apply a second and third time, that is troublesome; and I do not instruct the troublesome. There will be advantage in being firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
