      <prop type="x-segment-type">block</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">block</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 4 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 4 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六，發蒙，利用刑人，用說桎梏，以往吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, (has respect to) the dispelling of ignorance. It will be advantageous to use punishment (for that purpose), and to remove the shackles (from the mind). But going on in that way (of punishment) will give occasion for regret.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
