      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 4 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 4 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三，勿用取女，見金夫，不有躬，无攸利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, (seems to say) that one should not marry a woman whose emblem it might be, for that, when she sees a man of wealth, she will not keep her person from him, and in no wise will advantage come from her.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
