      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四，困蒙，吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, (shows its subject as if) bound in chains of ignorance. There will be occasion for regret.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
