      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五，童蒙，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject as a simple lad without experience. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
