      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 4 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 4 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九，擊蒙，不利為寇，利禦寇。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the topmost NINE, undivided, we see one smiting the ignorant (youth). But no advantage will come from doing him an injury. Advantage would come from warding off injury from him.</seg>
      </tuv>
